description: Deletes a build. This operation permanently deletes the build resource and any uploaded build files. Deleting a build does not affect the status of any active fleets using the build, but you can no longer create new fleets with the deleted build. To delete a build, specify the build ID. Upload a Custom Server Build. All APIs by task.

parameters.name: BuildId
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the build to delete. You can use either the build ID or ARN value.
